Package: sparseNumeric
Type: Package
Title: Sparse Numeric Vectors with Fast Algebra
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Arjun", "Kumar",
           email = "arjamikum@utexas.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an S4 class for sparse numeric vectors and
    methods for common vector operations without densifying,
    including addition, subtraction, elementwise multiplication,
    dot products, means, Euclidean norms, and standardization.
    Intended for teaching and lightweight sparse computations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
